DryadDataFile.dcterms:description: Table S1: Columns show species used for demographic reconstruction, citations for original studies, Bayesian Skyline Plot profiles and slopes, mutation rate priors (low and high locus mutation rate) used in hABC analyses, Ne priors (low and high Ne) used in hABC analyses, generation times with citations, and genetic summary statistics used in the hABC models. This file is a CSV file and can be opened for viewing in Excel, Google Sheets, or any other spreadsheet software.
